title.rendered: Louvre Beech Framed Stacking Side Chair

content.rendered:
The Louvre Side chair is a modern take on a traditional beech side chair. The Louvre chair has a polypropylene back and seat.

The Louvre chair stacks up to 4 high for ease of storage.

We offer the Louvre in 3 colours to suit your taste.

In stock for delivery in 3-5 working days.
